<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bottom-n">bottom <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bɒtəm/    美 /'bɑːtəm/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-base">1.★ <strong>［常用单数］底部；基部；最下部 (base)：</strong></h4>
<p>反 top </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>at the bottom of</strong> the page / list 
在页面/列表底部</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Bottoms up</strong>!
干杯！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are some tea leaves <strong>at / in the bottom of</strong> the cup.
杯底有一些茶叶</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>［单数］尽头；末端；底层：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>at the bottom of</strong> the garden 
在花园的尽头</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is always <strong>at the bottom of</strong> the class.
他在班上总是倒数第一。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>started at the bottom of</strong> the career. 
他从这项事业的最基层干起。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="from-the-bottom-of-ones-heart">from the bottom of one’s heart</h3>
<p>1.<strong>衷心地；发自内心地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>From the bottom of my heart, thank you. 
我从心底里感激你。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 3</footer></div></div>